\fs24 \cf0 Easy Downloader and Uploader 
\b0 is a very useful plugin if you want upload and download your file on your web server. This plugin makes downloading and uploading very easy. There are event system integrated.
\fs22 \
After integrating 
\b Easy Downloader and Uploader 
\b0 to your unity project you are ready to download and upload your files to the web server. If you are not integrated then look at the Integration.rtf file provided with this plugin.\
There is a DLL file at /Assets/Plugins/EasyDownloader.dll, this DLL have full functionality of the downloading and uploading. \
\

\b Default target directories for file to be saved after download-
\b0 \
Android = sdcard/Easy Downloader\
	
\i SDCard write permission should be given in player settings\

\i0 All other = Application.persistDatapath/Easy Downloader\

\i 	See Integration.rtf
\i0\b \
