\}\
2). Fired when upload finished.\
UploadAndDownload.onUploadComplete += OnUploadComplete;\
void OnUploadComplete()\
\{\
\}\
3). Fired if there is any error while downloading, uploading or writing to disk\
UploadAndDownload.onError += OnError;\
void OnError(string error)\
\{\
\}\
4). Fired while downloading is in progress. progress value will be between 0 to 1.\
UploadAndDownload.onProgress += OnProgress;\
